This repository contains the CP_AL and FA_CP algorithmic implementations,
experiment policies, benchmark wrappers, reproducibility checks, and
documentation used in "Restarted Reflected Halpern Acceleration for Augmented
Primal--Dual Methods".

The CP_AL and FA_CP algorithmic modifications and all release-specific material
are maintained by Benqi Liu. Portions of the low-level GPU infrastructure and
input utilities are redistributed under the Apache License 2.0. Their original
copyright notices remain in the corresponding source files. A consolidated
origin and modification record is provided in THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.

Names of external solvers appearing in benchmark scripts or result tables
identify comparison methods only. They are not names for the CP_AL or FA_CP
implementations released here.
